[
  {
    "text": "Here we are at the beach,",
    "start": 0,
    "end": 1500
  },
  {
    "text": "my favorite place to be.",
    "start": 1600,
    "end": 3000
  },
  {
    "text": "Mommy, can we go for a swim?",
    "start": 3100,
    "end": 5000
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't wait to splash in the sea.",
    "start": 5100,
    "end": 7000
  },
  {
    "text": "Roll out all the towels neatly on the sand.",
    "start": 7100,
    "end": 10000
  },
  {
    "text": "Put some sun cream on your back.",
    "start": 10100,
    "end": 12000
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me lend a hand.",
    "start": 12100,
    "end": 13500
  },
  {
    "text": "There, George.",
    "start": 13600,
    "end": 14500
  },
  {
    "text": "Sit right there.",
    "start": 14600,
    "end": 15500
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's your bucket and spade.",
    "start": 15600,
    "end": 17500
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't forget it gets quite hot.",
    "start": 17600,
    "end": 19500
  },
  {
    "text": "Best to have some shade.",
    "start": 19600,
    "end": 21000
  },
  {
    "text": "Pat, pat.",
    "start": 21100,
    "end": 22000
  },
  {
    "text": "Down we go.",
    "start": 22100,
    "end": 23000
  },
  {
    "text": "Gently on the top.",
    "start": 23100,
    "end": 24500
  },
  {
    "text": "Careful as you lift it off.",
    "start": 24600,
    "end": 26000
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't want it to flop.",
    "start": 26100,
    "end": 27500
  },
  {
    "text": "Splash, splash,",
    "start": 27600,
    "end": 28500
  },
  {
    "text": "here I go in my rubber ring.",
    "start": 28600,
    "end": 30500
  },
  {
    "text": "Gazing.",
    "start": 30600,
    "end": 31500
  },
  {
    "text": "Look up at clouds above.",
    "start": 31600,
    "end": 33000
  },
  {
    "text": "They could be anything.",
    "start": 33100,
    "end": 34500
  },
  {
    "text": "Look there in the sea.",
    "start": 34600,
    "end": 36000
  },
  {
    "text": "I can see a fin.",
    "start": 36100,
    "end": 37500
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't be scared.",
    "start": 37600,
    "end": 39000
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not a shock.",
    "start": 39100,
    "end": 40500
  },
  {
    "text": "Just daddy snorkeling.",
    "start": 40600,
    "end": 42000
  },
  {
    "text": "Down, down, down we go in a submarine.",
    "start": 42100,
    "end": 45000
  },
  {
    "text": "I wonder what we'll find out here",
    "start": 45100,
    "end": 47500
  },
  {
    "text": "peering through the screen.",
    "start": 47600,
    "end": 49000
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh gosh, what is that underneath? the sea.",
    "start": 49100,
    "end": 52000
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at that big friendly face staring back at me.",
    "start": 52100,
    "end": 56000
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time for a treat.",
    "start": 56100,
    "end": 57500
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we have ice cream?",
    "start": 57600,
    "end": 59500
  },
  {
    "text": "Watch that jinky seagull swoop.",
    "start": 59600,
    "end": 62000
  },
  {
    "text": "Watch out or I scream.",
    "start": 62100,
    "end": 63500
  },
  {
    "text": "Tutt.",
    "start": 63600,
    "end": 64500
  },
  {
    "text": "There he is flying overhead.",
    "start": 64600,
    "end": 66500
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you take my ice cream.",
    "start": 66600,
    "end": 68500
  },
  {
    "text": "He's mermaid instead.",
    "start": 68600,
    "end": 70500
  }
]